nodes.text: This male was the last boyfriend of New Republic Intelligence agent Yrica Quell. The two had a relationship at some point before Quell defected from the Imperial Starfighter Corps to the New Republic in 4 ABY. Quell reviewed the records of Alphabet Squadron's pilots with the IT-O Interrogator Unit droid IT-O; when reviewing her own records, she was willing to discuss anything, including her last boyfriend or first girlfriend, if it would convince the droid that she was fit to command the squadron.
